** Core principles

less is more  ==> less ui actions are good!!!! network/timeout/cloud/machine/stale element

Clear intention ==> make test cases atomic!!!! ui should  not be used to create test data!!!

Independent ===> test cases should be independent

Right Vs Wrong

Best Vs Worst ==>> when someone says its best practice , it cannot be best practice , maybe it needs update, bu nedenle best ve worst u kullanma!!!!

Good Vs Bad  ===> yerine iyi veya kotu olara k kullan

